msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Jo Amon! ...Him!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "The Amon Clan of assassins has been out to kill\r\nme for about ten years now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "For as many times as I've defeated him,\r\nyou'd think he'd have learned by now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "But if I ignore this, he'll find me when I least\r\nexpect him. I've got no choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "I should be able to take a taxi to his floating\r\nisland. This could be the fight of my life..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "It's been a while, Kazuma Kiryu.\r\nI've been waiting for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Defeating you is our clan's utmost desire...\r\nThe end has justified the means..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "And now it is time to defeat you and prove\r\nthe Amon Clan's superior strength!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Let's go, Kiryu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Tch... This cannot be..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Haven't I told you I'd take you down\r\nno matter how many times you tried?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Why..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "I've done everything by means\r\nboth fair and foul to grow stronger..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "I've defeated countless foes and trained\r\nunceasingly to become invincible..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "How can it be that I keep losing to you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Who cares."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Tch..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Hey, Amon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Isn't it time you came over to my side?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "...What are you saying?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "I'm building a clan these days, and we'd\r\nbe unstoppable with you among our ranks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Fool...! You think I am brought\r\nso low as to ally with you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "You'll have the opportunity to fight every day.\r\nDon't you want to get stronger? It's perfect."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "And if your aim is to take me out, wouldn't\r\nbeing closer to me make it easier to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Lend me your strength, Amon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "In exchange, you can ambush me whenever you feel\r\nthe need. Not that I'm going to let you win."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Fine then. Just know, it will eventually\r\nbecome apparent how foolish this decision is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "We're done here, then.\r\nWelcome aboard, Amon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Pah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Do not assume you can ever\r\ntame the Amon Clan..."
msgstr ""

